title: Renaissance - 1974 - Turn of the Cards
description:
Renaissance - 1974 - Turn of the Cards

(this is my first upload, so please bear with me)

"Turn of the Cards" is the best wotk of Renaissance and simply one of the best Prog/Art/Folk rock albums of all time. this is an absolute masterpiece of musicianship and songwriting and a fusion of classical, folk and rock music. It&#039;s a must for any prog rock fan or anyone interested in good music.
